ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of ALLAN DUNCAN ROWE of Trenton, Nova Scotia, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Denis Jacob.
